# ru.vec.bin (27.5 MB) and ru.probes.json are COMMITTED, not generated at build
# time: CI has no 192 MB araneum download, so an ignored asset would ship a
# semantic screen that 404s. Regeneration is byte-identical for a given input,
# but the blob does not delta-compress — each regeneration adds ~23 MB to the
# pack forever. Regenerate only when the lexicon or scoring actually changes.
